at you are willing to accept in your career.\n\n- Julieanne\n|\nAll your life you're yellow. Then one day you brush up against something blue, the barest touch, and voila, the rest of your life you're green.\n\n- Tess\n|\nShe let out a strangled laugh. “Yeah, that’s how it works. I just woke up one morning and was like, ‘gee, I want to screw Kyler.’ Seriously, you have no clue.\n\n- Jennifer Armentrout, Frigid\n|\nYou can either complain about it or grind, I choose to grind.\n\n- Kyle Vidrine, Wake Up The Winner In You: Your Time Is Now\n|\nI just met Stephen King in my dreams... I just said what I have watched and read from his books... Mainly I received a hug from him, it was like we are friends from long time.\n\n- Deyth\n|\nHow nice -- to feel nothing, and still get full credit for being alive.\n\n- Kurt Vonnegut Jr., Slaughterhouse-Five\n|\nIn your life, always be like a driver who runs the car not just a car.\n\n- Santosh"